{"tid":1757423,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"如果呢推同政治有關既人出現係以前tvb神魔歷史劇","createTime":"2019-11-26T13:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T13:07:32.000Z","uid":115041,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"89092fba64395c35dc7644c03438f7677357e052","tid":1757423,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:35:05.000Z","msg":"林鄭柒婆<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yF8aBtJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyF8aBtJ.png&h=7d502cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97BrUft.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97BrUft.jpg&h=087c0c4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天子尋龍 boss<br />\n實際上俾蜥蜴精假扮，好似柒婆咁，明明港英訓練出黎，依加奸撚到屌你老味要死全家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何已完<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fzAgw2K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfzAgw2K.jpg&h=1386bacf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c41vBux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc41vBux.jpg&h=a417a06a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回到三國條柒頭，有少少計以為自己好撚醒，又奸又賤正撚屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳雲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTe1H92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTe1H92.jpg&h=559a7bcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BUqoWvb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBUqoWvb.jpg&h=d7b02c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n通天教主，以為自己學完法術就想出山做國師，實際上唔撚掂，心術不正<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDHuR35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDHuR35.jpg&h=79429ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccymJaS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccymJaS.jpg&h=2db13e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曹操，奸奸地，會因為利益講人話<br />\n會欣賞敵人<br />\n單論能力都算係梟雄<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HvQz3bt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvQz3bt.jpg&h=5f57ed21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FtVL9Rz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFtVL9Rz.jpg&h=6c4e2713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係打得有能力，有腦，會同自己人反下面<br />\n俾敵人欣賞<br />\n<br />\n蕭山<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K6Hq9RZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6Hq9RZ.jpg&h=f9c42907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2L7e3b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2L7e3b5.jpg&h=457f3460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉細良<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u1BSPSf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1BSPSf.jpg&h=38d69dd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDyxPSm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDyxPSm.jpg&h=1e4de060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如來，表面睇人蓄無害，左膠一個，有啲智慧咁<br />\n但係，分分鐘係最奸嗰個，摸唔清，似有陰謀，好似背後操縱佛道之爭<br />\n<br />\n朱凱迪<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2j5qrv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2j5qrv.jpg&h=0aa3de75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SihuR6G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSihuR6G.jpg&h=e50b4ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太撚忠，左膠，死得早<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誠哥<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dm7KF0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDm7KF0c.jpg&h=325d275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地藏王菩薩<br />\n有啲勢力，講嘢唔敢講得太明顯<br />\n<br />\n仲有一推柒頭，真係諗唔到有邊個夠佢地奸<br />\n<br />\n李家超<br />\n盧偉聰<br />\n鄭若華<br />\n鄧炳強<br />\n<br />\n下列<br />\n中共<br />\n港共<br />\n黑警"},{"pid":"845d73338e143a4a6e912f095e02aea9e1e1b8d6","tid":1757423,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:38:09.000Z","msg":"譚惠珠 - 豬八戒"},{"pid":"4c715e31cb5d9081b0ccbdbebdd940484b